 significant increase suggesting CPU overload.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Median CPU usage rate increased from 29.34 to 92.01 with change ratio 1.0328.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate and MemAvailable_bytes indicated memory pressure.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Memory usage increased to 45.9, available memory reduced with change ratio 0.229.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_processes anomaly indicating potential lifecycle issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes changed to p99 of 2.0 with a change ratio of 0.6667.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max metrics showed high latency spikes.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from 88953.72 to 8830.37 with a p99 change ratio of 1.6388.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThese hypotheses should help guide further investigation into the root cause of the fault and aid in remediation efforts."}
